item.title: By: Ben

item.title: By: Ben
item.dc:creator: Ben
item.description: Thank you for commenting! It's always encouraging to hear from people who read the blog. =D I will work hard to continue providing quality posts so that you can continue to live vicariously through me! Though I hope that one day you and I will be able to play against one another!

item.title: By: Menoitios
item.dc:creator: Menoitios
item.description: Just a note from a reader to say thanks, great blog. I have enjoyed reading about your quest to improve your go --- I have been enjoying go vicariously through your excellent posts, as I have had no time to play seriously in the last year.

item.title: By: frandibar
item.dc:creator: frandibar
item.description: Hey Ben, don't stress, take it easy. This blog is your playground, not your work (am I wrong?). Remember that 'less is more', cheers.
